    "plain_content":  "RIGGERS Travel \u0026 Adventure\n\nHaving trouble viewing this email? Try *THIS LINK*.\n\n*NEW YEAR HOLIDAY TRAVEL*\n\nIt’s the end of the year, are you ready to celebrate the new year in a new place? Let RIGGERS provide you the most unforgettable experience!\n\n*SWITZERLAND*\n\nThe Swiss Alps is a stunning location to spend the New Year. If you\u0027re an avid skier or snowboarder and enjoy beautiful mountain views, then this is the trip for you.\n\nLEARN MORE\n\nLooking to escape the winter blues? Head to Thailand! With gorgeous beaches and incredible food, Thailand is the warm oasis you need.\n\nLEARN MORE\n\n*THAILAND*\n\n*MEXICO*\n\nIf you\u0027re looking for a metropolitan vacation, Mexico City is the perfect destination in January. Fewer crowds, mild temperatures, and a vibrant culture create a recipe for a great vacation.\n\nLEARN MORE\n\n( https://www.facebook.com/sendgrid/ ) ( https://www.instagram.com/sendgrid/ ) ( https://www.pinterest.com/sendgrid/ ) ( https://www.linkedin.com/company/sendgrid/ )\n\n{{Sender_Name}}\n\n{{Sender_Address}} , {{Sender_City}} , {{Sender_State}} {{Sender_Zip}}\n\nUnsubscribe ( {{{unsubscribe}}} )\n\n♥ POWERED BY TWILIO SENDGRID ( https://sendgrid.com/ )",
